‚ÄéYou want me to step down ‚Äéwhen I indicted him?

01:01:08.122 --> 01:01:10.708
‚ÄéI swear on my life ‚Äéthat I'll help you take over Reina.

01:01:10.792 --> 01:01:12.168
‚ÄéIf I reveal the truth about that,

01:01:12.251 --> 01:01:14.253
‚ÄéGrandma will give up the idea ‚Äéof letting you take over.

01:01:14.337 --> 01:01:15.880
‚ÄéI don't plan to wait for long.

01:01:15.963 --> 01:01:18.049
‚ÄéDispel the rumor yourself, ‚Äéwith a marriage.

01:01:19.509 --> 01:01:21.678
‚ÄéIt's Prosecutor Ma Gang-uk.

01:01:21.761 --> 01:01:23.513
‚Äé-Ms. Cheon? ‚Äé-Who are you?

01:01:23.596 --> 01:01:25.306
‚ÄéWe shared a bed.

01:01:25.390 --> 01:01:27.517
‚Äé-They must have a thing. ‚Äé-They're playing hard to get.

01:01:30.103 --> 01:01:32.063
‚ÄéWhy does he have my gloves?

01:01:32.146 --> 01:01:34.023
‚ÄéI did that without my gloves?

01:01:35.566 --> 01:01:40.029
‚ÄéDo you happen to see things ‚Äéyou weren't able to before?

01:01:43.908 --> 01:01:45.326
‚ÄéHe's in my home right now.

01:01:45.410 --> 01:01:46.786
‚ÄéHe came all the way to my home.

01:01:47.286 --> 01:01:52.208
‚ÄéSubtitle translation by: Jennifer Jean Lim

